---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="プラン加入" path="/subscription">
  <div slot="main" class="subscription-page">
    <header>
      <h1 class="page-title">プラン加入</h1>
      <p class="page-description">
        有料プランに加入して、限定コンテンツや特典をお楽しみください。
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="coming-soon-container">
      <div class="coming-soon-card">
        <div class="coming-soon-icon">🚀</div>
        <h2 class="coming-soon-title">有料プラン準備中</h2>
        <p class="coming-soon-description">
          現在、より充実したコンテンツをお届けするため<br>
          有料プランの準備を進めております。
        </p>
        <div class="coming-soon-features">
          <h3>提供予定の機能</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>プレミアム記事の閲覧</li>
            <li>限定動画コンテンツ</li>
            <li>メンバー限定コミュニティ</li>
            <li>オンラインセミナーへの参加</li>
            <li>個別相談・サポート</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="notify-section">
          <p>サービス開始のお知らせをご希望の方は<br>メールアドレスをご登録ください。</p>
          <div class="notify-form">
            <input type="email" placeholder="メールアドレスを入力" class="notify-input" disabled>
            <button class="notify-button" disabled>通知を受け取る</button>
          </div>
          <p class="notify-note">※ 現在準備中のため、通知登録は後日開始予定です</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="plans-preview">
      <h3>提供予定のプラン</h3>
      <div class="plans-container">
        <div class="plan-card preview" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">
          <div class="preview-badge">準備中</div>
          <div class="plan-header">
            <h2 class="plan-name">ベーシックプラン</h2>
            <div class="plan-price">
              <span class="price">¥500</span>
              <span class="period">/月（予定）</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="plan-features">
            <li>全ての記事の有料部分を閲覧可能</li>
            <li>限定動画コンテンツの視聴</li>
            <li>月1回の限定ウェビナー参加権</li>
            <li>コミュニティへの参加</li>
          </ul>
          <button class="plan-button" disabled>
            準備中
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="plan-card preview featured" style="animation-delay: 0.3s">
          <div class="preview-badge recommended">準備中</div>
          <div class="plan-header">
            <h2 class="plan-name">プレミアムプラン</h2>
            <div class="plan-price">
              <span class="price">¥1,200</span>
              <span class="period">/月（予定）</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="plan-features">
            <li>ベーシックプランの全特典</li>
            <li>月2回の限定ウェビナー参加権</li>
            <li>個別質問・相談の権利</li>
            <li>限定資料のダウンロード</li>
            <li>早期アクセス特典</li>
          </ul>
          <button class="plan-button primary" disabled>
            準備中
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="plan-card preview" style="animation-delay: 0.4s">
          <div class="preview-badge">準備中</div>
          <div class="plan-header">
            <h2 class="plan-name">エンタープライズ</h2>
            <div class="plan-price">
              <span class="price">¥3,000</span>
              <span class="period">/月（予定）</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="plan-features">
            <li>プレミアムプランの全特典</li>
            <li>月4回の限定ウェビナー参加権</li>
            <li>1対1メンタリングセッション</li>
            <li>カスタムコンテンツ制作</li>
            <li>優先サポート</li>
          </ul>
          <button class="plan-button" disabled>
            準備中
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="payment-info">
      <h3>お支払いについて</h3>
      <p>
        お支払いはStripeを通じて安全に処理されます。<br>
        クレジットカード、デビットカードをご利用いただけます。<br>
        いつでもキャンセル可能です。
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="subscription-help">
      <h3>よくある質問</h3>
      <div class="faq-container">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h4>いつでもキャンセルできますか？</h4>
          <p>はい、いつでもキャンセル可能です。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h4>支払い方法は？</h4>
          <p>クレジットカード、デビットカードでお支払いいただけます。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h4>領収書は発行されますか？</h4>
          <p>Stripeから自動的に領収書が発行されます。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .subscription-page {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }

  .page-title {
    color: var(--tobiracast-primary-blue);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out;
  }

  .page-description {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--tobiracast-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.1s both;
  }

  .plans-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .plan-card {
    background: var(--tobiracast-bg-primary);
    border: 2px solid var(--tobiracast-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out both;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
  }

  .plan-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--tobiracast-shadow-hover);
  }

  .plan-card.featured {
    border-color: var(--tobiracast-primary-orange);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--tobiracast-bg-primary) 0%, var(--tobiracast-bg-secondary) 100%);
  }

  .plan-card.preview {
    opacity: 0.7;
    position: relative;
  }

  .plan-card.preview button {
    cursor: not-allowed;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .preview-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    right: 20px;
    background: #999;
    color: white;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .preview-badge.recommended {
    background: var(--tobiracast-primary-orange);
  }

  .plan-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    right: 20px;
    background: var(--tobiracast-primary-orange);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  /* Coming Soon Section */
  .coming-soon-container {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out 0.2s both;
  }

  .coming-soon-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--tobiracast-primary-blue) 0%, var(--tobiracast-light-blue) 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: var(--tobiracast-card-shadow);
  }

  .coming-soon-icon {
    font-size: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    animation: bounce 2s infinite;
  }

  .coming-soon-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-shadow: var(--tobiracast-text-shadow-medium);
  }

  .coming-soon-description {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .coming-soon-features {
    background: var(--tobiracast-white-overlay-20);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .coming-soon-features h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .coming-soon-features ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .coming-soon-features li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .coming-soon-features li::before {
    content: "✨";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
  }

  .notify-section {
    background: var(--tobiracast-white-overlay-10);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .notify-section p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .notify-form {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
  }

  .notify-input {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.5;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }

  .notify-input::placeholder {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  }

  .notify-button {
    padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
    background: var(--tobiracast-primary-orange);
    color: white;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: bold;
    cursor: not-allowed;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .notify-note {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .plans-preview {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .plans-preview h3 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--tobiracast-primary-blue);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
  }

  .plan-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .plan-name {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--tobiracast-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .plan-price {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .price {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: var(--tobiracast-primary-blue);
  }

  .period {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--tobiracast-text-secondary);
  }

  .plan-features {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .plan-features li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .plan-features li::before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--tobiracast-primary-orange);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .plan-button {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 1rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--tobiracast-primary-blue);
    background: white;
    color: var(--tobiracast-primary-blue);
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .plan-button:hover {
    background: var(--tobiracast-primary-blue);
    color: white;
  }

  .plan-button.primary {
    background: var(--tobiracast-primary-orange);
    border-color: var(--tobiracast-primary-orange);
    color: white;
  }

  .plan-button.primary:hover {
    background: var(--tobiracast-dark-orange);
    border-color: var(--tobiracast-dark-orange);
  }

  .payment-info {
    background: var(--tobiracast-bg-secondary);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .payment-info h3 {
    color: var(--tobiracast-primary-blue);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .subscription-help {
    background: var(--tobiracast-bg-secondary);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .subscription-help h3 {
    color: var(--tobiracast-primary-blue);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .faq-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    background: var(--tobiracast-bg-primary);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--tobiracast-border);
  }

  .faq-item h4 {
    color: var(--tobiracast-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-item p {
    color: var(--tobiracast-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  /* Responsive Design */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .plans-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .plan-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .price {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>